{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":779,"text":"What do you think of when I say the word \"design\"?"},{"time":4500,"text":"You probably think of things like this,"},{"time":6820,"text":"finely crafted objects that you can hold in your hand,"},{"time":10331,"text":"or maybe logos and posters and maps"},{"time":13260,"text":"that visually explain things,"},{"time":15181,"text":"classic icons of timeless design."},{"time":18339,"text":"But I'm not here to talk about that kind of design."},{"time":21220,"text":"I want to talk about the kind"},{"time":22375,"text":"that you probably use every day"},{"time":24404,"text":"and may not give much thought to,"},{"time":26165,"text":"designs that change all the time"},{"time":28276,"text":"and that live inside your pocket."},{"time":30533,"text":"I'm talking about the design"},{"time":32596,"text":"of digital experiences"},{"time":34651,"text":"and specifically the design of systems"},{"time":37387,"text":"that are so big that their scale"},{"time":39020,"text":"can be hard to comprehend."},{"time":41111,"text":"Consider the fact that Google processes"},{"time":43372,"text":"over one billion search queries every day,"},{"time":47157,"text":"that every minute, over 100 hours"},{"time":49325,"text":"of footage are uploaded to YouTube."},{"time":51525,"text":"That's more in a single day"},{"time":53292,"text":"than all three major U.S. networks broadcast"},{"time":56042,"text":"in the last five years combined."},{"time":59317,"text":"And Facebook transmitting the photos,"},{"time":61621,"text":"messages and stories"},{"time":62817,"text":"of over 1.23 billion people."},{"time":65989,"text":"That's almost half of the Internet population,"},{"time":68733,"text":"and a sixth of humanity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71405,"text":"These are some of the products"},{"time":72419,"text":"that I've helped design over the course of my career,"},{"time":75173,"text":"and their scale is so massive"},{"time":77293,"text":"that they've produced unprecedented"},{"time":79181,"text":"design challenges."},{"time":81027,"text":"But what is really hard"},{"time":83389,"text":"about designing at scale is this:"},{"time":86120,"text":"It's hard in part because"},{"time":87956,"text":"it requires a combination of two things,"},{"time":90861,"text":"audacity and humility â€”"},{"time":93638,"text":"audacity to believe that the thing that you're making"},{"time":97482,"text":"is something that the entire world wants and needs,"},{"time":100778,"text":"and humility to understand that as a designer,"},{"time":103874,"text":"it's not about you or your portfolio,"},{"time":106314,"text":"it's about the people that you're designing for,"},{"time":108906,"text":"and how your work just might help them"},{"time":110802,"text":"live better lives."},{"time":112406,"text":"Now, unfortunately, there's no school"},{"time":115027,"text":"that offers the course Designing for Humanity 101."},{"time":119120,"text":"I and the other designers"},{"time":120692,"text":"who work on these kinds of products"},{"time":122436,"text":"have had to invent it as we go along,"},{"time":125788,"text":"and we are teaching ourselves"},{"time":127405,"text":"the emerging best practices"},{"time":129273,"text":"of designing at scale,"},{"time":131253,"text":"and today I'd like share some of the things"},{"time":133205,"text":"that we've learned over the years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135285,"text":"Now, the first thing that you need to know"},{"time":136516,"text":"about designing at scale"},{"time":137646,"text":"is that the little things really matter."},{"time":140620,"text":"Here's a really good example of how"},{"time":142557,"text":"a very tiny design element can make a big impact."},{"time":146060,"text":"The team at Facebook that manages"},{"time":149140,"text":"the Facebook \"Like\" button"},{"time":151248,"text":"decided that it needed to be redesigned."},{"time":153720,"text":"The button had kind of gotten out of sync"},{"time":156147,"text":"with the evolution of our brand"},{"time":157596,"text":"and it needed to be modernized."},{"time":159384,"text":"Now you might think, well, it's a tiny little button,"},{"time":161252,"text":"it probably is a pretty straightforward,"},{"time":163245,"text":"easy design assignment, but it wasn't."},{"time":166260,"text":"Turns out, there were all kinds of constraints"},{"time":168381,"text":"for the design of this button."},{"time":170190,"text":"You had to work within specific\nheight and width parameters."},{"time":173645,"text":"You had to be careful to make it work"},{"time":175940,"text":"in a bunch of different languages,"},{"time":177701,"text":"and be careful about using\nfancy gradients or borders"},{"time":180756,"text":"because it has to degrade gracefully"},{"time":182900,"text":"in old web browsers."},{"time":184653,"text":"The truth is, designing this tiny little button"},{"time":187325,"text":"was a huge pain in the butt."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189508,"text":"Now, this is the new version of the button,"},{"time":191560,"text":"and the designer who led this project estimates"},{"time":194074,"text":"that he spent over 280 hours"},{"time":197588,"text":"redesigning this button over the course of months."},{"time":201238,"text":"Now, why would we spend so much time"},{"time":203582,"text":"on something so small?"},{"time":205886,"text":"It's because when you're designing at scale,"},{"time":207502,"text":"there's no such thing as a small detail."},{"time":210631,"text":"This innocent little button"},{"time":212147,"text":"is seen on average 22 billion times a day"},{"time":216102,"text":"and on over 7.5 million websites."},{"time":219602,"text":"It's one of the single most viewed\ndesign elements ever created."},{"time":223686,"text":"Now that's a lot of pressure for a little button"},{"time":226190,"text":"and the designer behind it,"},{"time":227910,"text":"but with these kinds of products,"},{"time":229438,"text":"you need to get even the tiny things right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232174,"text":"Now, the next thing that you need to understand"},{"time":234710,"text":"is how to design with data."},{"time":237198,"text":"Now, when you're working on products like this,"},{"time":238870,"text":"you have incredible amounts of information"},{"time":241615,"text":"about how people are using your product"},{"time":243703,"text":"that you can then use to influence"},{"time":245358,"text":"your design decisions,"},{"time":246942,"text":"but it's not just as simple as following the numbers."},{"time":249694,"text":"Let me give you an example"},{"time":250945,"text":"so that you can understand what I mean."},{"time":253110,"text":"Facebook has had a tool for a long time"},{"time":255267,"text":"that allowed people to report photos"},{"time":257580,"text":"that may be in violation of our community standards,"},{"time":260442,"text":"things like spam and abuse."},{"time":262862,"text":"And there were a ton of photos reported,"},{"time":264870,"text":"but as it turns out,"},{"time":266506,"text":"only a small percentage were actually"},{"time":268402,"text":"in violation of those community standards."},{"time":271320,"text":"Most of them were just your typical party photo."},{"time":273830,"text":"Now, to give you a specific hypothetical example,"},{"time":276738,"text":"let's say my friend Laura hypothetically"},{"time":279234,"text":"uploads a picture of me"},{"time":280892,"text":"from a drunken night of karaoke."},{"time":283880,"text":"This is purely hypothetical, I can assure you."},{"time":287146,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":288641,"text":"Now, incidentally,"},{"time":290410,"text":"you know how some people are kind of worried"},{"time":291700,"text":"that their boss or employee"},{"time":293343,"text":"is going to discover embarrassing photos of them"},{"time":295350,"text":"on Facebook?"},{"time":296890,"text":"Do you know how hard that is to avoid"},{"time":298826,"text":"when you actually work at Facebook?"},{"time":302080,"text":"So anyway, there are lots of these photos"},{"time":304366,"text":"being erroneously reported as spam and abuse,"},{"time":307800,"text":"and one of the engineers on the team had a hunch."},{"time":310249,"text":"He really thought there was something else going on"},{"time":312376,"text":"and he was right,"},{"time":313532,"text":"because when he looked\nthrough a bunch of the cases,"},{"time":315856,"text":"he found that most of them"},{"time":317456,"text":"were from people who were requesting"},{"time":319331,"text":"the takedown of a photo of themselves."},{"time":322153,"text":"Now this was a scenario that the team"},{"time":324193,"text":"never even took into account before."},{"time":326560,"text":"So they added a new feature"},{"time":328369,"text":"that allowed people to message their friend"},{"time":330513,"text":"to ask them to take the photo down."},{"time":332785,"text":"But it didn't work."},{"time":334244,"text":"Only 20 percent of people"},{"time":335495,"text":"sent the message to their friend."},{"time":337713,"text":"So the team went back at it."},{"time":339964,"text":"They consulted with experts in conflict resolution."},{"time":343155,"text":"They even studied the universal principles"},{"time":346217,"text":"of polite language,"},{"time":347704,"text":"which I didn't even actually know existed"},{"time":349239,"text":"until this research happened."},{"time":351176,"text":"And they found something really interesting."},{"time":353705,"text":"They had to go beyond just helping people"},{"time":355888,"text":"ask their friend to take the photo down."},{"time":357800,"text":"They had to help people express to their friend"},{"time":360529,"text":"how the photo made them feel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362960,"text":"Here's how the experience works today."},{"time":365158,"text":"So I find this hypothetical photo of myself,"},{"time":368385,"text":"and it's not spam, it's not abuse,"},{"time":371014,"text":"but I really wish it weren't on the site."},{"time":373537,"text":"So I report it and I say,"},{"time":376761,"text":"\"I'm in this photo and I don't like it,\""},{"time":378801,"text":"and then we dig deeper."},{"time":382063,"text":"Why don't you like this photo of yourself?"},{"time":384569,"text":"And I select \"It's embarrassing.\""},{"time":387416,"text":"And then I'm encouraged to message my friend,"},{"time":390742,"text":"but here's the critical difference."},{"time":392601,"text":"I'm provided specific suggested language"},{"time":396233,"text":"that helps me communicate to Laura"},{"time":398569,"text":"how the photo makes me feel."},{"time":400504,"text":"Now the team found that this relatively small change"},{"time":403545,"text":"had a huge impact."},{"time":405224,"text":"Before, only 20 percent of people"},{"time":407624,"text":"were sending the message,"},{"time":408795,"text":"and now 60 percent were,"},{"time":410840,"text":"and surveys showed that people"},{"time":412474,"text":"on both sides of the conversation"},{"time":414402,"text":"felt better as a result."},{"time":416042,"text":"That same survey showed"},{"time":417697,"text":"that 90 percent of your friends"},{"time":420050,"text":"want to know if they've done something to upset you."},{"time":422788,"text":"Now I don't know who the other 10 percent are,"},{"time":424885,"text":"but maybe that's where our \"Unfriend\" feature"},{"time":426659,"text":"can come in handy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":428220,"text":"So as you can see,"},{"time":429994,"text":"these decisions are highly nuanced."},{"time":432602,"text":"Of course we use a lot of data"},{"time":434571,"text":"to inform our decisions,"},{"time":435882,"text":"but we also rely very heavily on iteration,"},{"time":439325,"text":"research, testing, intuition, human empathy."},{"time":443449,"text":"It's both art and science."},{"time":445295,"text":"Now, sometimes the designers\nwho work on these products"},{"time":447861,"text":"are called \"data-driven,\""},{"time":449549,"text":"which is a term that totally drives us bonkers."},{"time":452290,"text":"The fact is, it would be irresponsible of us"},{"time":455189,"text":"not to rigorously test our designs"},{"time":457741,"text":"when so many people are counting on us"},{"time":459827,"text":"to get it right,"},{"time":461020,"text":"but data analytics"},{"time":463340,"text":"will never be a substitute for design intuition."},{"time":466442,"text":"Data can help you make a good design great,"},{"time":469610,"text":"but it will never made a bad design good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":473234,"text":"The next thing that you need\nto understand as a principle"},{"time":476346,"text":"is that when you introduce change,"},{"time":477893,"text":"you need to do it extraordinarily carefully."},{"time":480499,"text":"Now I often have joked that"},{"time":482166,"text":"I spend almost as much time"},{"time":484404,"text":"designing the introduction of change"},{"time":486218,"text":"as I do the change itself,"},{"time":488418,"text":"and I'm sure that we can all relate to that"},{"time":490714,"text":"when something that we use a lot changes"},{"time":492754,"text":"and then we have to adjust."},{"time":494986,"text":"The fact is, people can become"},{"time":497190,"text":"very efficient at using bad design,"},{"time":500130,"text":"and so even if the change is\ngood for them in the long run,"},{"time":502802,"text":"it's still incredibly frustrating when it happens,"},{"time":505859,"text":"and this is particularly true"},{"time":507666,"text":"with user-generated content platforms,"},{"time":510362,"text":"because people can rightfully\nclaim a sense of ownership."},{"time":513803,"text":"It is, after all, their content."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517406,"text":"Now, years ago, when I was working at YouTube,"},{"time":519773,"text":"we were looking for ways to"},{"time":521968,"text":"encourage more people to rate videos,"},{"time":524244,"text":"and it was interesting because\nwhen we looked into the data,"},{"time":526970,"text":"we found that almost everyone was exclusively using"},{"time":530429,"text":"the highest five-star rating,"},{"time":532396,"text":"a handful of people were using"},{"time":533980,"text":"the lowest one-star,"},{"time":535656,"text":"and virtually no one"},{"time":537075,"text":"was using two, three or four stars."},{"time":539405,"text":"So we decided to simplify"},{"time":541300,"text":"into an up-down kind of voting binary model."},{"time":544624,"text":"It's going to be much easier\nfor people to engage with."},{"time":547620,"text":"But people were very attached"},{"time":550172,"text":"to the five-star rating system."},{"time":551965,"text":"Video creators really loved their ratings."},{"time":554396,"text":"Millions and millions of people"},{"time":555618,"text":"were accustomed to the old design."},{"time":557781,"text":"So in order to help people"},{"time":559716,"text":"prepare themselves for change"},{"time":561420,"text":"and acclimate to the new design more quickly,"},{"time":563653,"text":"we actually published the data graph"},{"time":566116,"text":"sharing with the community"},{"time":567836,"text":"the rationale for what we were going to do,"},{"time":569984,"text":"and it even engaged the larger industry"},{"time":572605,"text":"in a conversation, which resulted in"},{"time":574070,"text":"my favorite TechCrunch headline of all time:"},{"time":577148,"text":"\"YouTube Comes to a 5-Star Realization:"},{"time":580612,"text":"Its Ratings Are Useless.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":583640,"text":"Now, it's impossible to completely avoid"},{"time":586295,"text":"change aversion when you're making changes"},{"time":588795,"text":"to products that so many people use."},{"time":590923,"text":"Even though we tried to do all the right things,"},{"time":592530,"text":"we still received our customary flood"},{"time":594763,"text":"of video protests and angry emails"},{"time":597387,"text":"and even a package that had\nto be scanned by security,"},{"time":601635,"text":"but we have to remember"},{"time":603595,"text":"people care intensely about this stuff,"},{"time":606435,"text":"and it's because these products, this work,"},{"time":609373,"text":"really, really matters to them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":611593,"text":"Now, we know that we have to be careful"},{"time":614900,"text":"about paying attention to the details,"},{"time":616890,"text":"we have to be cognizant about how we use data"},{"time":619363,"text":"in our design process,"},{"time":621035,"text":"and we have to introduce change"},{"time":622840,"text":"very, very carefully."},{"time":624531,"text":"Now, these things are all really useful."},{"time":626627,"text":"They're good best practices for designing at scale."},{"time":629739,"text":"But they don't mean anything"},{"time":631531,"text":"if you don't understand something"},{"time":633203,"text":"much more fundamental."},{"time":634865,"text":"You have to understand who you are designing for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639626,"text":"Now, when you set a goal to design"},{"time":641363,"text":"for the entire human race,"},{"time":643229,"text":"and you start to engage in that goal in earnest,"},{"time":646283,"text":"at some point you run into the walls"},{"time":648707,"text":"of the bubble that you're living in."},{"time":650755,"text":"Now, in San Francisco, we get a little miffed"},{"time":653395,"text":"when we hit a dead cell zone"},{"time":654979,"text":"because we can't use our phones to navigate"},{"time":656628,"text":"to the new hipster coffee shop."},{"time":659123,"text":"But what if you had to drive four hours"},{"time":662277,"text":"to charge your phone"},{"time":663613,"text":"because you had no reliable source of electricity?"},{"time":666854,"text":"What if you had no access to public libraries?"},{"time":670309,"text":"What if your country had no free press?"},{"time":673133,"text":"What would these products start to mean to you?"},{"time":676873,"text":"This is what Google, YouTube and Facebook"},{"time":679617,"text":"look like to most of the world,"},{"time":681336,"text":"and it's what they'll look like"},{"time":682394,"text":"to most of the next five billion people"},{"time":684496,"text":"to come online."},{"time":686056,"text":"Designing for low-end cell phones"},{"time":688322,"text":"is not glamorous design work,"},{"time":690689,"text":"but if you want to design for the whole world,"},{"time":692601,"text":"you have to design for where people are,"},{"time":694712,"text":"and not where you are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":696465,"text":"So how do we keep this big, big picture in mind?"},{"time":699632,"text":"We try to travel outside of our bubble to see, hear"},{"time":702716,"text":"and understand the people we're designing for."},{"time":705291,"text":"We use our products in non-English languages"},{"time":707667,"text":"to make sure that they work just as well."},{"time":709820,"text":"And we try to use one of these\nphones from time to time"},{"time":712955,"text":"to keep in touch with their reality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715891,"text":"So what does it mean to design at a global scale?"},{"time":720168,"text":"It means difficult and sometimes exasperating work"},{"time":723582,"text":"to try to improve and evolve products."},{"time":727554,"text":"Finding the audacity and the\nhumility to do right by them"},{"time":730747,"text":"can be pretty exhausting,"},{"time":732110,"text":"and the humility part,"},{"time":733622,"text":"it's a little tough on the design ego."},{"time":735826,"text":"Because these products are always changing,"},{"time":738298,"text":"everything that I've designed in my career"},{"time":740810,"text":"is pretty much gone,"},{"time":742106,"text":"and everything that I will design will fade away."},{"time":745386,"text":"But here's what remains:"},{"time":747162,"text":"the never-ending thrill"},{"time":749114,"text":"of being a part of something that is so big,"},{"time":751962,"text":"you can hardly get your head around it,"},{"time":754695,"text":"and the promise that it just might change the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":757592,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":759990,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}